              <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl">About NSBA</h2>
              <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
                North Sound Bicycle Advocates (NSBA) is a not-for-profit, all-volunteer group representing bicycle riders in North King and South Snohomish counties.</p>
                <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">Our goal is to promote greater use of bikes for utility, transportation and recreation; to promote safer and more welcoming conditions for all bike riders; and to advocate for a seamless system of connected bike routes to enable trips by bike across our region.</P>
